review_blob: Bottle. labatts version of a budget beer. you definetly get what you pay for with this beer! if you just want to get drunk then this is the beer for you
Bottle and tap this beer is definetly an ale, but not as enjoyable as a hand crafted beer. i still do prefer it over molson export.
Bottle and tape. being from barrie i am not being bias to the beer, but it is a good quality micro brew. unique flavor and taste, worth the cost?

Creemore Springs is on of the highest quality micro brews i have every tasted. the flavour and aroma are very unique. this beer is widley avaliable in ontario. hope the rest of the world can enjoy it as easily some day.
